description:
intermodulation distortion of a bipolar rf power transistor, measured according to the two-tone test method, as a variable.
Two-tone test method: |f_1 = 28.000 MHz, V_1 = V_o - 6 dB f_2 = 28.001 MHz, V_2 = V_o - 6 dB |measured harmonic component is: (f_2 + 1 kHz) - (f_1 - 1 kHz) = 3 kHz.
